tattoos of his own slamm learned his trade at new yorks coney 
island during the 1950s when the process was still legal doing his 
first tattoo when he was 12 
whitney a former construction worker got into the business 
three years ago after he was injured on his old job 
though theyre business rivals whitney who wears 20 tattoos 
and slamm have artistic respect for each other slamm is working on 
a jungle scene that will eventually cover whitneys back it 
features a panther leaping through the flesh into a forest of 
tangled vines and waiting predators 
both men plan to hire assistants so they can keep up with 
peoples demand for colorful unicorns dragons daggers and 
